The auxiliary CR room is a somewhat long room with 30 chambers in
three rows.  The door opens facing the side of the middle row.

Salveo: Please use the back row of machines.  I&#39;m taking the first one.

Salveo walked up to the machine and pressed a button.  The hatch-like
door swung upward allowing him to get inside.  The machine closed.

Meanwhile...

Perseus took the message from the trooper and thanked him.

Perseus:  We need to address this right away.  However, I really need
to use a CR.  Please give this go Guardia.  Tell her that i need her
to respond to this distress call and determine the situation.  She&#39;s
in her quarters.

Meanwhile....

Trelos seemed intrigued by Blacknightmare&#39;s response.

Trelos:  So, you serve Unicron.  Why would you be interested in what
that overgrown glutton-bot wants?

Trelos twitched and sparked.  He leaned over for a second as if in
pain before regaining his composure.

